T1  - Effect of acupuncture and metformin on insulin sensitivity in women with polycystic ovary syndrome and insulin resistance: a three-armed randomized controlled trial.
T3  - Comment in: Hum Reprod. 2022 May 3;37(5):1097. doi: 10.1093/humrep/deac055 PMID: 35333322 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/35333322] Comment in: Hum Reprod. 2022 May 3;37(5):1098-1100. doi: 10.1093/humrep/deac056 PMID: 35333327 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/35333327]
